Legislation may lay down exhaustive requirements for applications for participation in procurement.
In the autumn session at the plenary session, the State Duma is planning to consider in second reading a bill setting out requirements for the content and composition of the application for participation in the procurement, to which only small and medium-sized enterprises may participate.
Amendments are made by the government to the law "On procurement of goods, works, services by separate types of legal entities".
The bill was drafted in accordance with the Roadmap for the Implementation of the Strategy for the Development of Small and Medium Enterprises in the Russian Federation until 2030, approved by the Government.
