Degtyarev surprised information about the purchase of gas "Sakhalin-1" for the dollar
Interim Governor of the Khabarovsk region Mikhail Degtyarev on Sunday, July 26, during a meeting with residents of Soviet Havana was surprised that the region was buying Sakhalin gas from the American company Exxon Neftegas for dollars.
