Woman drops her husband's body in a pit and pours concrete under Belgorod
In Belgorod region, the woman confessed to the murder of her own husband, which she threw in a pit with waste and poured concrete, reported on the website of the regional administration of the Russian Federation.
It is noted that the suspect has been married to the murdered since 1999.
In recent years, the husband began to abuse alcohol and after another dispute, the woman decided to murder.
“When the husband fell asleep, the suspect tied his arms and legs, put a plastic bag on his head, and squeezed it with a pillow.
When the husband stopped giving signs of life, she turned her body into a carpet, took it out into the yard and hid it in a crawling pit.
The next day, she called the concrete mixer and poured the well with concrete,” the department said.
The woman later reported that her husband had disappeared.
The relatives of the deceased turned to the police, who opened the pit and pulled the body.
The investigation is intended to request the arrest of the suspect.
The criminal case is currently being investigated.
