Singer Polina Gagarina Calls for Helping Weight Loss Products
Russian singer Polina Gagarina named five products that helped her adjust the figure and not later gain weight again.
The first on the list was water.
The singer prefers to drink clean, non-gasic water before each meal in order to suffocate the feeling of hunger and eat less.
Also ideal for maintaining stiffness will be vegetable salad, fried rice and seafood.
Thanks to them, it is possible to prepare a balanced diet: vegetables contain fiber, rice contains complex carbohydrates, and seafood is a source of protein, useful vitamins and amino acids.
For unloading days, the singer chooses apples.
Thanks to these products, Gagarina was able to get rid of 30 extra pounds.
In addition, the singer switched to a small diet - eating often and slightly and excluded fat, sweet and calorie from the diet.
Gagarina does not eat roasted food, baked goods, sausages and other meat semi-finished, writes kp.ru on July 26.
She also replaced red meat with fish and seafood.
Prefers vegetables (other than potatoes), whole grains and a lot of greens.
Gagarina is also active in the gym, yoga and running.
